39:59.100 --> 40:00.120
I am just telling them

40:00.200 --> 40:03.720
with hypocrisy with a double standard you cannot manage Sahaja Yoga.

40:03.720 --> 40:06.040
You cannot cheat yourself, you cannot cheat others.

40:06.360 --> 40:08.820
Cheating is not allowed. If you do cheating,

40:08.940 --> 40:10.920
you will cheat your Kundalini.

40:11.040 --> 40:12.480
Kundalini knows everything.

40:17.160 --> 40:19.700
[Marathi]

47:44.920 --> 47:49.480
Leaders should never make importance of their wives or their husbands, not at all.

47:49.900 --> 47:53.580
Otherwise you ruin us completely.

47:53.980 --> 47:55.760
Or we might have to take out a rule that

47:55.760 --> 47:58.760
nobody who has a wife or a husband is going to be a leader.

47:58.980 --> 48:01.580
One of the two things or children.

48:03.800 --> 48:06.040
It’s terrible it is sometimes.
